### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/

### Login (sample credentials: admin/admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Paste token from login response
@token = paste_token_here

### Protected: Prizes list
GET http://localhost:8080/prizes?year=2023&category=physics&limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Protected: Prize details
GET http://localhost:8080/prizes/2023/physics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Protected: Prize laureates
GET http://localhost:8080/prizes/2023/physics/laureates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
